            review: 'This class took a lot more work than I expected, but was well worth it. The pace started out extremely fast, but slowed down a little after a few weeks. Very well organized, great TAs, and Dr. Joyner was always available.  There is a group project which can be hit or miss. Fortunately I had a great group. The concepts were immediately useful in my day to day job.',
